metadata.name: CHIME SVIIvR
metadata.description: Version of the CHIME model that extedns the core SIR dynamics to add vaccination (V) and vaccinated but infected (Iv) compartments.Maintains pre-computation of simple policy affecting relative contact rate and its impact on infection rate (beta).

bibjson.title: CHIME: COVID-19 Hospital Impact for Epidemics - Online Documentation
